2002-06-04  rprix  <rprix@microwave>

	* /local/cvsRep/FD/FreeDroid/src/map.c, /local/cvsRep/FD/FreeDroid/src/ship.c:
	Improved lift algorithm: first blit ship "lights off", then
	blit active level and lift-row rectangles from "lights on" ship-picture,
	then update screen. --> Results look&feel much more "stable".

	* /local/cvsRep/FD/FreeDroid/src/blocks.c, /local/cvsRep/FD/FreeDroid/src/global.h, /local/cvsRep/FD/FreeDroid/src/graphics.c, /local/cvsRep/FD/FreeDroid/src/init.c, /local/cvsRep/FD/FreeDroid/src/map.c, /local/cvsRep/FD/FreeDroid/src/misc.c, /local/cvsRep/FD/FreeDroid/src/proto.h:
	some code cleanup: *completely* removed obsolete variables
	RealScreen, InternalScreen, Outline320x200 , together with
	old block display functions Display*Block().

	* /local/cvsRep/FD/FreeDroid/src/ship.c, /local/cvsRep/FD/FreeDroid/src/graphics.c:
	some cleanup in the lift code and picture.
	(don't forget to "install" new pics)

