	Had some sound problems:  The very first sound call of freedroid seems
	to be always completely ignored??? THIS REMAINS UNEXPLAINED.

	* /local/cvsRep/FD/FreeDroid/src/bullet.c, /local/cvsRep/FD/FreeDroid/src/defs.h, /local/cvsRep/FD/FreeDroid/src/influ.c, /local/cvsRep/FD/FreeDroid/src/init.c, /local/cvsRep/FD/FreeDroid/src/misc.c, /local/cvsRep/FD/FreeDroid/src/rahmen.c, /local/cvsRep/FD/FreeDroid/src/sound.c, /local/cvsRep/FD/FreeDroid/src/text.c:
