	* /local/cvsRep/FD/FreeDroid/src/init.c:
	erroneous #include of nonexistent "paths.h" removed. (sorry)

2002-05-26  jprix  <jprix@microwave>

	* /local/cvsRep/FD/FreeDroid/src/SDL_rotozoom.c, /local/cvsRep/FD/FreeDroid/src/enemy.c, /local/cvsRep/FD/FreeDroid/src/graphics.c, /local/cvsRep/FD/FreeDroid/src/influ.c, /local/cvsRep/FD/FreeDroid/src/main.c, /local/cvsRep/FD/FreeDroid/src/map.c, /local/cvsRep/FD/FreeDroid/src/proto.h, /local/cvsRep/FD/FreeDroid/src/view.c:
	Erradicated some warnings.
