	* /local/cvsRep/FD/FreeDroid/src/sound.c:
	deleted more unused sound code.  improved debug logging a little bit more.

	* /local/cvsRep/FD/FreeDroid/src/sound.c:
	added more doku to sound.c and remove some old unused code.

